longBusinessSummary: Mensch und Maschine Software SE provides computer aided design, manufacturing, and engineering (CAD/CAM/CAE), product data management, and building information modeling/management solutions in Germany and internationally. It operates in two segments, VAR Business and M+M Software. The VAR Business segment sells CAD software to end users, as well as provides associated services. The M+M Software segments develops CAD/CAM/CAE software. The company offers software solutions that are used for the process control of milling, drilling, and turning in various industries, such as mechanical engineering; tool, mold, and die making; automotive and aerospace industry; medical technology; and toy industry, as well as watch, clock, and jewelry manufacturing. Mensch und Maschine Software SE was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Starnberg, Germany.
